%F A279283 G.f.: x * (1 - x)^12 / (1 - 5*x + 6*x^2 - 4*x^3 + x^4)^4.
%F A279283 From _Seiichi Manyama_, May 19 2026: (Start)
%F A279283 G.f.: x * (B(x)/x)^4, where B(x) is the g.f. of A055988.
%F A279283 a(n) = Sum_{k=1..n} binomial(k+2,3) * binomial(n+3*k-1,4*k-1). (End)
%t A279283 CoefficientList[Series[x (1 - x)^12/(1 - 5 x + 6 x^2 - 4 x^3 + x^4)^4, {x, 0, 25}], x]
